Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:29.16,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an9}想い出を掻き集めてるだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.19,0:22:34.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an9}少しずつの　すれ違いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.13,0:22:39.25,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an9}いつの間に二人を別つ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.32,0:22:44.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an9}綾なす樹々に降る細雪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.65,0:22:49.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an9}満ちては欠けてゆく月の光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.88,0:22:55.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an9}見渡す一面に雪化粧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.53,0:23:00.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an9}全て包む様に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:05.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an9}何処かに落としてきた情熱も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.02,0:23:11.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an9}誰かを愛した日の温もりも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.34,0:23:16.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an9}二度とは戻れない日々だって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.88,0:23:23.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an9}過ぎてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.54,0:22:23.42,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an7}思念緩緩滑過指間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:29.16,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an7}我只是想收集和你的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.19,0:22:34.08,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an7}一點一點的錯過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.13,0:22:39.25,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an7}不知不覺 已將兩人分離
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.32,0:22:44.54,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an7}降落於瑞樹上的細雪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.65,0:22:49.78,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an7}盈滿後漸漸缺損的月光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.88,0:22:55.43,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an7}眼前一片銀裝素裹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.53,0:23:00.45,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an7}彷彿將一切包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:05.82,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an7}往日的激情不知散落何處
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.02,0:23:11.22,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an7}與某人相愛時的那份溫存
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.34,0:23:16.81,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an7}也已經一去不返 這樣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.88,0:23:23.15,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}{\an7}還會不斷繼續
